OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter Romsey 'fight'
OL,6,FOfficers investigating a stabbing in
OL,7,FRomsey have charged a man.
OL,9,FHampshire Police were called to
OL,10,FTreviglio Close at 3.56pm on Friday,
OL,11,F22 May, to reports of fighting.
OL,13,FA man in his 50s was found with stab
OL,14,Fwounds.
OL,16,FHe was taken to hospital for treatment.
