OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter Romsey 'fight'
OL,6,FDaniel Eric Carter, 41, of Treviglio
OL,7,FPlace in Romsey, has been charged with
OL,8,Fattempted murder, criminal damage,
OL,9,Fassaulting an emergency worker, and
OL,10,Fpossession of a knife or bladed
OL,11,Farticle in a public place.
OL,13,FHe appeared before Southampton
OL,14,FMagistrates Court today, 25 May, where
OL,15,Fhe was further remanded.
OL,17,FHe is next due to appear before
OL,18,FSouthampton Crown Court on 26 June.
